:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抵制TVB去影視台 連儂牆去活動台 得唔得呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307891\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307891</a></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b80c47ca22f166f05715770d6ad3ed113ae92765","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1167483f4d272fbbad25a7a2f2727d9bde890a21","tid":1307971,"uid":266969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a4633a7fa0eb954eb52fafed1aad07b384a6950","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:31:48.000Z","msg":"冇錯你守牆，同啲藍絲／廢老嘈，搏佢哋出手打你，可以爭取到光環<br />\n但係光環究竟有冇作用都仲未知，你就已經周身傷<br />\n都唔使講之後有咩行動你可能因為傷得滯參與唔到<br />\n<br />\n成日都講只貼不守，有人要拆就畀佢拆，睇佢拆得幾多<br />\n我明白大家可能為咗幅牆花咗好多心思，但係呢啲係講象徵意義<br />\n為咗啲隨時都可以翻生嘅象徵意義送頭，你諗清楚究竟值唔值啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:35:41.000Z","msg":"forward from tg<br />\n對家零成本嘛<br />\n退休警打完你去赤柱渡下假，長糧照咬<br />\n廢老郁完你，佢都唔使搵工咬老綜既，怕乜？<br />\n<br />\n相反，你還手（講真好佩服打不還手，比我應該同佢死過），一係兩邊捉晒，對家退休留案底，OR 本身就案底厚過棟IFC，你就無端端倒蝕比佢<br />\n<br />\n如果黑警叫你唔好告，一告就兩邊拉晒，你都白蝕比人佢打一餐，今日仲有人手都比人打斷<br />\n<br />\n另一方面蝕埋觀感，本身應該係和理非活動，而家個觀感變左有牆=有交打"},{"pid":"15cc4acaf7f4037c651e406a453a0e129e045b94","tid":1307971,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:36:55.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"300451b3ebe9c4d0da81c5b3f327a9c0de4fa0bd","tid":1307971,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:37:11.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b061f20f27af4a451fe54670ca1aa838abb5e45e","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"不受傷不流血<br />\n好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ad7dddc933670de5a2d21ad07eb35b4fe5fb90","tid":1307971,"uid":65196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"推，變返傳單啦"},{"pid":"6de51d90d388e85365baaeb308eb7bea768dc7c0","tid":1307971,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:37:36.000Z","msg":"連儂牆唔止係打飛機，仲可以接觸群眾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307937</a><br />\n<br />\n唔洗守，但可以幫連儂牆升級"},{"pid":"14d4ace6345def36b67a6a5294597a29eef16873","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:38:16.000Z","msg":"不受傷不流血<br />\n好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec9e91c2f9cd8a8fd46026c7304c1ece0ace40a","tid":1307971,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"我傾向認同嘅，但好多人為呢樣嘢已經自我分化緊<br />\n心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【團結】無大台嘅抗爭，我哋應該無時無刻激烈咁互屌。但冷靜之後要記得我哋係同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305309</a>"},{"pid":"54027c364c6e0a4c11a6453e86fb0f9ab560425b","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58182563b18a4f38aaf9813b5eeec7e5520420d","tid":1307971,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a39a9bdd5f7895e8f440fd1ee1ae22384806b7b6","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56aeed8f7841a6a3957771e47f1bf2a0679075d9","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5316b8acfe2cca17d281906e9f0280e7a4b7ee7a","tid":1307971,"uid":219277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:46:17.000Z","msg":"其實今晚斷手骨果個呀叔<br />\n佢係自己衝左上去指罵果隻撕紙狗<br />\n撕紙狗出手捉佢手, 跟住已經受傷<br />\n事前成班人都淨係圍觀, 拍片同屌, 應該無諗住送頭<br />\n但你好難阻止有人突然衝動要埋身去屌鳩班藍屍<br />\n大埔單野只係5-6秒內就發生同結束<br />\n可能當事人都無諗過會打交, 只係諗住挑釁<br />\n<br />\n不過俾人打到跌低果位黑帶巴打嘅行為就真係送頭啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a7a4e1bd63361ba5df6d34eee148fd85a359e3","tid":1307971,"uid":278759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:50:29.000Z","msg":"大家幫手喺地區谷做呼籲啦，叫啲人唔好再硬撼<br />\n贏光環，輸士氣。對家知你任打任砌，一定越玩越紅，而我哋就係中晒破窗寒蟬<br />\n由得佢哋今晚拆，我哋聽日起囉"},{"pid":"9457e87051049a6ed4d8d6ee322fc947c9fc5a25","tid":1307971,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e408a43b4774b9196bf497836a640ba6cda19f80","tid":1307971,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:58:30.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好守嘅<br />\n有幾多個喺現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你教我點做<br />\n<br />\n情景:<br />\n有20個人圍觀，痴牆睇野影相<br />\n突然有一個人衝過黎屌你，迫開你撕野<br />\n咁你點?<br />\n全部人彈開望住佢撕?<br />\n<br />\n之後後面有個街坊睇唔過眼屌佢<br />\n佢屌返轉頭<br />\n屌屌下就推撞<br />\n又點算<br />\n<br />\n更甚者，好似今晚<br />\n你整整下野佢就衝過黎直接打你<br />\n前晚5秒之內<br />\n你又可以點做?<br />\n<br />\n個氣氛冇可能佢一個走過黎<br />\n現場2-30人一窩鋒全部走哂<br />\n衝突好難避免架"}]}